snippet.description:
Bamboo stores water in its hollow segments for survival. From my observations, you can find this water in young stalks, particularly those near water sources or after prolonged heavy rains. The water undergoes natural filtration through the plant's roots and tissues, giving it a slightly sweet taste and making it drinkable. The young bamboo tissue is quite easy to pierce with a knife. Simply make one or two holes (at the top and bottom) to enjoy the refreshing bamboo water!

snippet.title: Sajjan Raj Vaidya - Ghumi Phiri [Official Release]
snippet.description:
And so, I became yours, before I was even myself. The melody wrote the words, the words sang the melody, as if everything was to always return to find me as yours. As time refused to change directions, space bent itself to place me in front of you so I could fall in love the way love was meant to be fallen into.

In one way or the other, in some time or another, as I have found myself in front of you, I shall always find myself as yours.

For Maya, always.

snippet.description:
बालेन र वडाध्यक्षको डरलाग्दो चर्काचर्की - सडक बिभाग र न्युरोडको बिषयले लियो उग्ररुप  Balen Shah News | Mahanagr Baithak | Today News | Wave Nepal
#balenshah #todaysnews #wavenepal
